import './Roadmap.css'; import React from 'react'; export const Roadmap = () => { return (
THE GAME PLAN
Building an inter-connected community is our number one priority. We strive for greatness and embrace risk-taking, hustling and seizing every moment.
PRE-MINT PHASE
Fortune favors the brave, and we are a community for the brave. Our goal pre-mint is to create and foster a community where people encourage one another to win and thrive. We are the pioneers of the Web3 space, the Ballers of the digital world. Our main objective is to incubate a community and give the members as much value as possible. Once our team of Ballers is formed we’ll move forward as a united front to show rest of the world what we can do.
PRE-MINT PHASE
Baller Games To grow closer as a community and reward our holders (Ballers), we’ll be hosting fun, interactive games and giveaways. Ballers will compete in weekly tournaments for NFTs, ETH Prizes and whitelist opportunities. Our goal is to create friendships between ballers for mutual personal and financial development. Ballers-Only Event (+2 guest) The in-person Ballers-Only Event will be filled with giveaways and other Baller fun. This will be an opportunity to connect on a deeper level as a community and encourage greater connectivity among Ballers.
); };
